====== PURPOSE ======
== Generates features for SDSS Stripe 82 light curves
The file ending in '.py' is the python script for extracting various features (Periods, Colors etc.), which can be directly run from the ‘FeatureExtraction’ folder of the master directory (stripe82-class-master)
The Jupyter notebook files (.ipynb) are intended to display the features extracted. 

====== USAGE ======
cd stripe82-class-master
cd FeatureExtraction
python PeriodColorExtraction.py
